1
00:00:55,000 --> 00:01:00,000
The Story of Minglan

2
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:02,825
Episode 8

3
00:01:19,640 --> 00:01:21,880
It hurts. Hurts.

4
00:01:22,360 --> 00:01:24,240
Eldest Brother is so tenacious.

5
00:01:24,960 --> 00:01:26,400
A few days ago,

6
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:27,600
he wanted to bribe my maidservants to his side.

7
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:29,160
He wanted to find out

8
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:30,280
where I set up my mistress.

9
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:31,560
I saw through his tricks.

10
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:32,900
And today

11
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:34,280
he's got you following me.

12
00:01:35,080 --> 00:01:36,600
It seems Eldest Brother's tricks

13
00:01:36,630 --> 00:01:38,360
are getting more and more skilled.

14
00:01:39,360 --> 00:01:40,320
Second Young Master! Second Young Master.

15
00:01:40,320 --> 00:01:41,040
I won't dare ever again!

16
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:43,200
You won't ever dare?

17
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:45,400
Then for what happened today,

18
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:47,120
what do you choose between a beating or a penalty?

19
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:49,360
I'll take a penalty.

20
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,680
penalty? Fine.

21
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:54,400
Then you leave the Marquis Manor

22
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:55,360
and find your own survival means.

23
00:01:56,040 --> 00:01:57,840
Never to speak to a Gu household member again!

24
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:02,720
Well, that . . .

25
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:03,680
What's wrong?

26
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:06,200
You can't part from the good fare

27
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:07,320
from the Marquis Manor?

28
00:02:08,200 --> 00:02:10,400
Second Master, I'll go with a beating.

29
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:12,160
A beating, really?

30
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:15,240
Then take three punches from Shitou.

31
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:15,800
Shitou!

32
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:17,480
Alright!

33
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:28,160
Look carefully.

34
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:33,160
Second Master. I'll go with the penalty.

35
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:34,080
Here,

36
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:35,560
I'll leave the Marquis Manor today, right away!

37
00:02:36,200 --> 00:02:37,960
No, I'll leave Bianjing City today

38
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:39,200
and never return!

39
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:55,600
We've beaten this one away

40
00:02:55,600 --> 00:02:56,800
yet another might come soon.

41
00:02:58,920 --> 00:03:00,480
We can only improvise with

42
00:03:00,480 --> 00:03:01,720
what may come.

43
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:03,960
Kicking one away is one difficult solved.

44
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,160
Once I make my scholarly honour,

45
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:09,000
Manniang can see the light of the world.

46
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:15,480
Be careful of your own health.

47
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:18,200
Eldest, don't be so anxious.

48
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:23,080
Someone came to report to me

49
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:24,560
that the servant came back

50
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:26,160
and started to pack up right away.

51
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:27,800
He's asked to go

52
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:29,160
to our Gu ancestral fields.

53
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:30,800
It’s obvious that Second Brother

54
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,640
already discovered we had someone tracking him,

55
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:34,160
and we've alerted him.

56
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,400
In the future,

57
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:38,840
if we want to find that woman

58
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:39,480
he's keeping,

59
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:41,040
it'll just get harder.

60
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,320
And my health is like this.

61
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:49,240
I don't know

62
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:50,920
if i can make it through the end of the year.

63
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:52,960
How can I not fret?

64
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:55,920
Second Son is usually most gentle.

65
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:58,920
He at most just skips classes,

66
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:00,480
drink some wine and use up all the money,

67
00:04:00,480 --> 00:04:02,200
or small matters like ridding a horse in the streets.

68
00:04:03,440 --> 00:04:05,440
Since he's known that woman,

69
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:07,080
he's been completely bewitched by her

70
00:04:08,880 --> 00:04:10,880
and raises two children too!

71
00:04:12,320 --> 00:04:14,080
If we don't find this woman

72
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:15,400
and dismiss her soon,

73
00:04:16,080 --> 00:04:16,720
I don't know how

74
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:18,120
she will ruin Second Brother later.

75
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,360
Where's Tingwei?

76
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:25,200
He has wide connections

77
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:27,120
and knows many loafing lordlings.

78
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:29,550
Maybe we can find out

79
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:31,000
Ye'er's information from them?

80
00:04:31,400 --> 00:04:32,600
Don't mention him anymore.

81
00:04:33,520 --> 00:04:34,720
That real son of mine

82
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:36,960
is the biggest oaf who is completely immature!

83
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:40,000
That day he saw that Second Son was beaten harshly.

84
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:42,120
he started to cry along several bouts.

85
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:44,800
I thought he would follow Darling Second

86
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:46,640
to do a bit learning.

87
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:50,320
But now he overrates himself,

88
00:04:50,320 --> 00:04:52,040
and starts to do the poetry club.

89
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:56,440
My health won’t last.

90
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:59,880
If later on Darling Second

91
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:01,360
is not doing his duty again,

92
00:05:01,880 --> 00:05:03,640
Tingwei will be the Marquis of Ningyuan.

93
00:05:04,520 --> 00:05:06,360
Why can't he cultivate his temperament

94
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:07,520
and go to school now?

95
00:05:07,880 --> 00:05:09,080
Stop the nonsense.

96
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,440
You're just frail.

97
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:14,040
That's not a major illness.

98
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:17,880
You're not allowed to speak so ominously.

99
00:05:17,880 --> 00:05:18,600
Got it?

100
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:45,400
Stop there.

101
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:55,720
It’s you again!

102
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:57,600
It wasn't me.

103
00:05:57,600 --> 00:06:00,120
Last time, I already told you.

104
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:02,480
When you come to work in our house,

105
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:04,720
no one is allowed to doll up herself.

106
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:08,520
Today, not only are you dressed like this,

107
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:10,840
but also you've loosened

108
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:11,920
your hair down,

109
00:06:12,440 --> 00:06:14,160
putting up the seductress look.

110
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:17,760
I guess your brain was eaten by a dog,

111
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:19,840
and you didn't remember my words?

112
00:06:19,840 --> 00:06:21,160
No, not so.

113
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:23,920
Duchess. Big Madam!

114
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,440
Forgive me.

115
00:06:25,440 --> 00:06:26,725
forgive me this time.

116
00:06:26,725 --> 00:06:27,885
I will never dare again!

117
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:36,400
Last time I saw you like this,

118
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:38,480
I already spared you once.

119
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:41,920
This time, you repeat the offense knowingly.

120
00:06:42,200 --> 00:06:44,360
That made the offense doubly guilty.

121
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:46,880
Go find someone

122
00:06:47,540 --> 00:06:49,640
and sell

123
00:06:49,640 --> 00:06:50,360
this shameless wench.

124
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:53,280
No,please don't!

125
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,440
Please forgive me!

126
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:55,600
Please forgive me.

127
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:56,850
I won't go.

128
00:06:56,960 --> 00:06:58,160
It's useless even if you cry.

129
00:06:58,160 --> 00:06:59,040
Please forgive me!

130
00:06:59,330 --> 00:07:00,720
Even if you're crying like this,

131
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:03,120
The Young Lord in the study over there,

132
00:07:03,790 --> 00:07:05,520
has he come out to take a look at you?

133
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:07,880
No, please!

134
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:10,160
Princess,

135
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,280
Princess!

136
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:12,880
Don't you think I don't know

137
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:14,280
what your schemes are.

138
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,400
You want to dress yourself as a seductress and

139
00:07:17,250 --> 00:07:18,840
wish for the day that

140
00:07:18,840 --> 00:07:20,960
the Young Lord can see you and take you in,

141
00:07:21,880 --> 00:07:23,320
and you soar to the sky with one step

142
00:07:23,320 --> 00:07:25,040
and become the mistress of the ducal house?

143
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,560
That’s a daydream!

144
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:30,280
You all listen carefully.

145
00:07:30,390 --> 00:07:32,080
Send my instructions.

146
00:07:32,080 --> 00:07:34,080
Especially these

147
00:07:34,080 --> 00:07:36,040
newly-arrived girls,

148
00:07:36,050 --> 00:07:37,200
be clever.

149
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:39,960
I grew up in the palace.

150
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:42,560
I've seen all sorts of tricks.

151
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,480
Don't play any tricks on me.

152
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:47,360
If I find out

153
00:07:48,280 --> 00:07:49,480
someone has tried to lure

154
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,760
and ruin my son,

155
00:07:51,520 --> 00:07:52,880
I will have you arrive vertically,

156
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:54,280
but leave here horizontally.

157
00:07:54,760 --> 00:07:57,280
Yes, we shall mark your teaching.

158
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,080
Mother.

159
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:28,200
What are you looking at all night

160
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:30,080
that you don't even turn a page?

161
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:33,400
Is there something golden?

162
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:37,000
I saw a sentence on this page

163
00:08:37,520 --> 00:08:38,025
and it reminded me

164
00:08:38,025 --> 00:08:39,160
of a query set out by the Academy Scholar.

165
00:08:39,800 --> 00:08:41,810
I was puzzling over it.

166
00:08:41,920 --> 00:08:43,480
A query?

167
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:44,440
What query?

168
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,625
Let me hear it.

169
00:08:46,640 --> 00:08:49,400
Let Mother help you think it through.

170
00:08:50,560 --> 00:08:51,400
No need.

171
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:56,120
Don't disregard your mother.

172
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:57,960
I have had a tutor

173
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:59,760
since I was young too.

174
00:09:00,160 --> 00:09:02,800
My education is not lower than you and your father.

175
00:09:03,920 --> 00:09:05,280
Which words

176
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:06,600
and what query?

177
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:07,640
Tell me.

178
00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:10,920
Speaking of learning,

179
00:09:11,640 --> 00:09:13,400
I have been

180
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:14,520
studying for quite some time at Sheng’s house now.

181
00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:15,880
I've bothered them quite a bit.

182
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:18,680
Mother, how about this?

183
00:09:18,880 --> 00:09:19,550
Tomorrow,

184
00:09:19,550 --> 00:09:21,520
you come with me to pay a visit

185
00:09:21,520 --> 00:09:22,680
to the Sheng Old Madam and

186
00:09:22,680 --> 00:09:24,280
bring some light gifts as a token of our gratitude.

187
00:09:24,280 --> 00:09:25,120
What do you think about that?

188
00:09:26,640 --> 00:09:28,400
When you started to go to to the Sheng's to study,

189
00:09:28,920 --> 00:09:30,720
your father already went there.

190
00:09:30,880 --> 00:09:32,280
And we've sent many gifts there already.

191
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:35,120
By rights,

192
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,480
we are a ducal house.

193
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:39,840
Sheng House is a house of a fifth-rank official.

194
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:43,120
It’s humbling ourselves in making acquaintances like this.

195
00:09:43,760 --> 00:09:45,200
And it would seem quite affected

196
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,600
if we frequent their house.

197
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:49,000
Others will feel like as if that

198
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:50,800
we are seeking something intentionally.

199
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:54,600
What could we seek there?

200
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:55,460
There's the saying that

201
00:09:55,460 --> 00:09:57,640
you can't fault someone for being too cordial.

202
00:09:58,440 --> 00:10:00,720
You're a child

203
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:03,800
who never cares for social visits before.

204
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:07,320
But today, how is it that you are interested?

205
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:10,400
Unless there's a story to it?

206
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,520
Mother, what do you mean?

207
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:15,720
Your son's grown.

208
00:10:16,560 --> 00:10:18,360
As for social visits,

209
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:19,800
I should have more understanding.

210
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:23,200
It's nice for my son to have this thought.

211
00:10:24,280 --> 00:10:25,400
The rest

212
00:10:25,400 --> 00:10:27,080
your father and I will see to.

213
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:29,600
Once you place at the top and make a name,

214
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:31,960
it's not too late to socialize then.

215
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:37,560
Mother. Just make the trip, please?

216
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:40,560
I'm not feeling well lately

217
00:10:40,560 --> 00:10:41,920
and my face is so haggard.

218
00:10:42,400 --> 00:10:43,920
How can I meet anyone

219
00:10:43,920 --> 00:10:45,400
with this face?

220
00:10:46,680 --> 00:10:48,400
Mother, you're already

221
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:49,440
the most beautiful woman on earth.

222
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:53,160
If you are unsightly,

223
00:10:53,160 --> 00:10:53,800
then no woman

224
00:10:53,800 --> 00:10:54,840
is sightly.

225
00:11:01,640 --> 00:11:02,880
You, child.

226
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:06,000
Why do you insist that I go to the Sheng house?

227
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:08,640
What do you plot?

228
00:11:12,640 --> 00:11:13,920
What can I plot?

229
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:16,280
I just wanted Mother

230
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:18,120
to be more involved in my learning.

231
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:21,360
I care for you most tenderly.

232
00:11:21,760 --> 00:11:22,240
Look.

233
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:24,560
This is all made specially for you.

234
00:11:26,520 --> 00:11:28,280
During this exam period,

235
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,320
you should just focus on studying.

236
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:33,120
The rest, don't over-think it.

237
00:11:52,320 --> 00:11:54,040
Princess, did you find

238
00:11:54,040 --> 00:11:55,120
something suspicious?

239
00:11:58,160 --> 00:11:59,280
He was holding a book,

240
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:01,400
but his eyes were looking elsewhere.

241
00:12:02,680 --> 00:12:04,520
Reflecting on the literature and questions?

242
00:12:05,920 --> 00:12:09,600
It seems more likely there's someone in his heart.

243
00:12:11,180 --> 00:12:12,315
Princess,

244
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:13,720
should we deal with this inside?

245
00:12:14,760 --> 00:12:17,520
There's many people here in the hallways.

246
00:12:18,560 --> 00:12:21,080
That's exactly what I want.

247
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,160
Have them all watch this.

248
00:12:35,920 --> 00:12:37,080
My respects, Princess.

249
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:38,600
For what have you requested my presence?

250
00:12:50,120 --> 00:12:54,240
When Young Master was studying at the Sheng's study,

251
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:57,400
did he talk to the daughters

252
00:12:57,400 --> 00:12:58,480
of the Sheng family?

253
00:12:59,760 --> 00:13:01,400
Of course he did,

254
00:13:02,160 --> 00:13:03,480
but he didn't say much either.

255
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:06,320
Master Scholar Zhuang keeps a tight schedule.

256
00:13:06,880 --> 00:13:07,800
They were busy and didn't have much time to talk.

257
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:10,480
Think carefully again before you speak.

258
00:13:11,440 --> 00:13:13,240
In the event

259
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:15,370
that I ever find out

260
00:13:15,440 --> 00:13:16,960
that you are not telling the truth,

261
00:13:17,480 --> 00:13:18,800
you know the consequences.

262
00:13:19,650 --> 00:13:21,400
Everything is true, nothing has been falsified.

263
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:23,200
Big Madam, you may inquire as you wish.

264
00:13:23,880 --> 00:13:25,520
Today, the three daughters of the Sheng family

265
00:13:25,520 --> 00:13:27,040
didn't even show up.

266
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:29,213
I heard that it's because they sought a nanny

267
00:13:29,213 --> 00:13:30,320
to teach them etiquette.

268
00:13:30,320 --> 00:13:30,813
Likely they won't even

269
00:13:30,813 --> 00:13:32,760
be able to meet anyone in the future.

270
00:13:32,760 --> 00:13:34,640
Then

271
00:13:34,640 --> 00:13:38,520
this Sheng's is cultured and steeped in propriety?

272
00:13:39,760 --> 00:13:41,080
Yes. That's right.

273
00:13:42,130 --> 00:13:44,200
The Young Master treats you well.

274
00:13:45,040 --> 00:13:46,360
If you want to be good to him,

275
00:13:47,100 --> 00:13:48,280
you should tell me the truth.

276
00:13:51,660 --> 00:13:52,520
If you just go along with him, you will do him no good.

277
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:54,720
I understand.

278
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:55,360
I have always looked out

279
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:56,400
for his interest.

280
00:13:57,760 --> 00:13:59,800
You don't need to be that scared.

281
00:13:59,800 --> 00:14:00,760
Leave now.

282
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:02,240
Yes.

283
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:14,240
Utter nonsense.

284
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:16,600
He's up to something.

285
00:14:16,600 --> 00:14:19,160
He's not telling the truth.

286
00:14:21,680 --> 00:14:23,200
The Sheng family has three daughters.

287
00:14:25,840 --> 00:14:27,600
I know what's

288
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:28,680
in their mind.

289
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:31,760
We can replace who's accompanying Young Master.

290
00:14:33,040 --> 00:14:34,600
Don't do it. He's used to him.

291
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:35,574
Since he was little until now,

292
00:14:35,574 --> 00:14:36,760
he has been with him and is very loyal.

293
00:14:37,680 --> 00:14:40,320
Moreover, the examination is due shortly.

294
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:43,000
If nothing terrible happens,

295
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:43,880
it's better not to take any actions

296
00:14:44,840 --> 00:14:45,840
and not create any scenes.

297
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:48,680
I'm afraid it will affect his future prospects.

298
00:15:10,040 --> 00:15:12,760
Nanny. You are finally here.

299
00:15:12,880 --> 00:15:13,880
I don't have to worry now that you are here.

300
00:15:15,240 --> 00:15:16,520
I found this house for you.

301
00:15:17,320 --> 00:15:18,480
Tianshui Alley.

302
00:15:19,090 --> 00:15:21,200
The name is nice and the geomancy here is good too.

303
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:24,680
This house is very stylish

304
00:15:24,680 --> 00:15:26,360
but I don’t need it.

305
00:15:26,360 --> 00:15:27,200
Why not?

306
00:15:31,120 --> 00:15:32,510
From now on

307
00:15:32,520 --> 00:15:33,800
you are the owner.

308
00:15:34,540 --> 00:15:35,720
They will listen to your instructions.

309
00:15:36,640 --> 00:15:38,240
You must take good care of Nanny.

310
00:15:38,240 --> 00:15:38,960
You must not be disrespectful.

311
00:15:39,840 --> 00:15:40,560
Yes.

312
00:15:43,640 --> 00:15:45,320
Come,Nanny,

313
00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:46,120
you have been wearied by your travel.

314
00:15:46,280 --> 00:15:47,840
Sit for a bit and rest.

315
00:15:48,040 --> 00:15:49,280
No need for rest.

316
00:15:49,720 --> 00:15:50,280
I'm not fit

317
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:52,000
to be a Mistress of a house.

318
00:15:55,040 --> 00:15:56,680
I set out on a long journey

319
00:15:56,680 --> 00:15:59,200
to share your worries and burdens.

320
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:04,040
Nanny, you had been serving my mother.

321
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:07,240
You have toiled for many years

322
00:16:07,240 --> 00:16:08,800
in the Bai family.

323
00:16:09,560 --> 00:16:10,920
You should enjoy a free and easy life now.

324
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:14,200
Even more so since I'm an adult now

325
00:16:14,200 --> 00:16:15,520
and I have people to serve me.

326
00:16:16,360 --> 00:16:17,480
I don't need to trouble you anymore.

327
00:16:18,360 --> 00:16:19,800
Young Master,

328
00:16:19,800 --> 00:16:21,560
don't underestimate this old woman.

329
00:16:21,880 --> 00:16:23,880
I'm still sturdy and strong.

330
00:16:24,120 --> 00:16:26,360
It's not a problem to work for another twenty years.

331
00:16:28,280 --> 00:16:30,360
Furthermore, you need someone

332
00:16:30,360 --> 00:16:32,440
who's considerate and caring.

333
00:16:35,160 --> 00:16:37,640
Alright. Nanny, say no more.

334
00:16:37,640 --> 00:16:38,800
I have decided.

335
00:16:46,280 --> 00:16:49,040
Nanny. Frankly

336
00:16:50,640 --> 00:16:52,960
there's a reason why I don't want you to live in

337
00:16:52,960 --> 00:16:54,080
the Manor of the Marquis.

338
00:16:55,800 --> 00:16:58,040
It's for your illegitimate child and that mistress?

339
00:16:59,400 --> 00:17:02,960
Never mind. As long as she's pure and kind,

340
00:17:03,560 --> 00:17:04,760
and is genuine

341
00:17:04,760 --> 00:17:07,400
and sincere to you, it's good enough.

342
00:17:07,640 --> 00:17:08,640
Of course.

343
00:17:08,840 --> 00:17:10,520
Manniang is naturally pure, kind,

344
00:17:10,520 --> 00:17:11,480
warm and caring.

345
00:17:12,280 --> 00:17:13,120
It's just that

346
00:17:15,040 --> 00:17:16,040
she doesn't have a good family background.

347
00:17:16,880 --> 00:17:18,080
When she was destitute,

348
00:17:18,080 --> 00:17:19,240
she was a minstrel for a short while.

349
00:17:19,520 --> 00:17:20,440
She won't be able to enter the Manor of the Marquis.

350
00:17:21,480 --> 00:17:22,560
What?

351
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:28,480
Young Master, you were so muddle-headed!

352
00:17:29,760 --> 00:17:30,480
You...

353
00:17:31,520 --> 00:17:34,440
Nanny, at the time,

354
00:17:34,840 --> 00:17:35,840
when I saw her

355
00:17:35,840 --> 00:17:36,560
being bullied

356
00:17:36,560 --> 00:17:37,600
in the street,

357
00:17:37,600 --> 00:17:38,630
I couldn't not help helping her.

358
00:17:38,720 --> 00:17:40,520
But I didn't expect

359
00:17:40,520 --> 00:17:41,280
she'd follow me

360
00:17:41,320 --> 00:17:42,480
all the way to Bailudong.

361
00:17:43,320 --> 00:17:44,480
Her elder brother died too.

362
00:17:45,200 --> 00:17:46,920
Then

363
00:17:48,520 --> 00:17:50,080
there were children.

364
00:17:52,520 --> 00:17:53,880
I know you are very angry

365
00:17:54,410 --> 00:17:57,360
but the mistake has already been committed.

366
00:17:57,960 --> 00:17:59,880
These two kids are innocent.

367
00:18:01,240 --> 00:18:02,400
Nanny,

368
00:18:02,400 --> 00:18:04,520
since I lost my mother when I was young,

369
00:18:05,760 --> 00:18:07,240
just help me.

370
00:18:09,600 --> 00:18:12,440
Fine. You are the master and I'm the servant.

371
00:18:12,840 --> 00:18:14,240
You want to keep a concubine

372
00:18:14,240 --> 00:18:15,680
and you even have children.

373
00:18:16,960 --> 00:18:20,520
How can this old woman not help you out?

374
00:18:22,640 --> 00:18:24,480
Nanny, you dote on me the most.

375
00:18:25,680 --> 00:18:26,520
By the way,

376
00:18:26,520 --> 00:18:28,960
does your father know about this?

377
00:18:31,240 --> 00:18:32,120
He knows.

378
00:18:33,520 --> 00:18:34,560
Not only does he know,

379
00:18:34,560 --> 00:18:35,440
But also he beat up Young Master

380
00:18:35,560 --> 00:18:36,920
because of this!

381
00:18:38,400 --> 00:18:40,000
Did he beat you severely?

382
00:18:40,000 --> 00:18:40,960
Let me take a look.

383
00:18:41,080 --> 00:18:42,160
It's not severe, Nanny.

384
00:18:43,040 --> 00:18:44,200
I applied medicine this morning.

385
00:18:44,200 --> 00:18:46,240
It's not visible anymore.

386
00:18:46,640 --> 00:18:47,960
What do you mean?

387
00:18:47,960 --> 00:18:48,840
It's bleeding.

388
00:18:49,000 --> 00:18:50,120
The swelling is this huge.

389
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:53,800
No, I want to see

390
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:55,200
how bad the beating is.

391
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:57,725
Luckily I brought medicine for sprain,

392
00:18:57,725 --> 00:19:00,080
bruises and migraines.

393
00:19:00,280 --> 00:19:01,520
I'm going to get it.

394
00:19:01,520 --> 00:19:02,160
Nanny, no!

395
00:19:02,160 --> 00:19:03,560
You wait here.

396
00:19:30,280 --> 00:19:32,200
I have been waiting for many days.

397
00:19:32,200 --> 00:19:34,320
You are finally here.

398
00:19:37,040 --> 00:19:38,440
Greetings, Nanny Kong.

399
00:19:40,680 --> 00:19:41,360
These are our

400
00:19:41,400 --> 00:19:43,080
two mediocre daughters.

401
00:19:43,680 --> 00:19:44,640
Being pampered since young

402
00:19:44,640 --> 00:19:45,960
and inexperienced.

403
00:19:46,480 --> 00:19:48,000
If they are not prepared for what's out there,

404
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:49,920
on account of their age, Nanny

405
00:19:49,920 --> 00:19:51,160
please slowly guide them.

406
00:19:51,670 --> 00:19:53,120
You can scold or beat them.

407
00:19:53,120 --> 00:19:55,320
As their mother, I will not dote on them.

408
00:19:56,080 --> 00:19:58,120
Big Madam, you are overly-modest.

409
00:19:58,120 --> 00:19:59,000
The two young Misses

410
00:19:59,000 --> 00:20:01,000
are girls from a respectable and educated family,

411
00:20:01,360 --> 00:20:03,560
their bearing and poise are naturally exceptional.

412
00:20:04,480 --> 00:20:05,600
I have only served

413
00:20:05,659 --> 00:20:08,059
in the palace for a few years

414
00:20:08,200 --> 00:20:10,680
and experienced a bit more than others,

415
00:20:10,680 --> 00:20:11,440
knowing something

416
00:20:11,440 --> 00:20:13,200
about tea-brewing and incense appreciation.

417
00:20:13,680 --> 00:20:15,480
If the Misses are willing to learn,

418
00:20:15,480 --> 00:20:18,200
I shall teach all without reservation.

419
00:20:18,760 --> 00:20:20,520
Quickly say your thanks to Nanny!

420
00:20:23,120 --> 00:20:24,240
Thank you, Nanny.

421
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:28,720
Everyone, please be seated.

422
00:20:41,240 --> 00:20:41,960
This..!

423
00:20:45,360 --> 00:20:46,800
Madam has something going on.

424
00:20:46,800 --> 00:20:48,400
Mistress Lin, you should go back.

425
00:20:49,920 --> 00:20:51,400
I have something important to report to Big Madam.

426
00:20:51,400 --> 00:20:52,350
I will leave when I'm done

427
00:20:52,350 --> 00:20:53,360
No need.

428
00:20:53,360 --> 00:20:54,480
Madam said that

429
00:20:54,480 --> 00:20:55,400
this Nanny is here to teach proprieties

430
00:20:55,400 --> 00:20:57,120
to the two Misses.

431
00:20:57,520 --> 00:20:59,480
The Fourth Miss is always so proper and courteous,

432
00:20:59,520 --> 00:21:00,520
gentle and virtuous.

433
00:21:00,920 --> 00:21:03,040
Since she has never stepped out of line before,

434
00:21:03,040 --> 00:21:04,720
she doesn't need further etiquette lessons.

435
00:21:05,360 --> 00:21:06,720
It's not appropriate to say this.

436
00:21:06,720 --> 00:21:08,040
They are all daughters of the Sheng family.

437
00:21:08,120 --> 00:21:09,700
This is favoring one and slighting the other.

438
00:21:09,720 --> 00:21:10,200
Exactly!

439
00:21:10,600 --> 00:21:12,040
I'm an uneducated person.

440
00:21:12,040 --> 00:21:13,600
I don't understand what this means.

441
00:21:13,800 --> 00:21:15,120
I'm only here to relay the main Mistress' message.

442
00:21:15,120 --> 00:21:16,680
If you still refuse to leave

443
00:21:18,960 --> 00:21:19,480
Someone.

444
00:21:19,520 --> 00:21:20,160
You...

445
00:21:22,920 --> 00:21:24,520
You,you!

446
00:21:29,320 --> 00:21:31,000
Let's see if this yard belongs to “Sheng”

447
00:21:31,000 --> 00:21:31,840
or "Lin" !

448
00:21:34,280 --> 00:21:35,640
Filthy witch.

449
00:21:35,640 --> 00:21:36,600
Though she calls herself the Madam

450
00:21:36,600 --> 00:21:37,880
but she is not acting like one!

451
00:21:38,120 --> 00:21:39,240
So afraid that my Mo'er

452
00:21:39,240 --> 00:21:40,760
will steal her daughter's prestige!

453
00:21:41,000 --> 00:21:42,040
Mistress, don't be angry.

454
00:21:42,040 --> 00:21:43,320
We will have other solutions.

455
00:21:44,080 --> 00:21:45,240
My poor Mo'er,

456
00:21:45,240 --> 00:21:46,400
she was born from me.

457
00:21:46,560 --> 00:21:47,760
If I was the Madam of the house，

458
00:21:47,760 --> 00:21:48,680
I wouldn't have to worry

459
00:21:48,680 --> 00:21:49,780
about her future like this.

460
00:21:49,840 --> 00:21:50,460
Exactly!

461
00:21:50,520 --> 00:21:52,320
I will get her into Nanny Kong's class

462
00:21:52,360 --> 00:21:53,320
no matter what!

463
00:21:53,360 --> 00:21:55,000
We will definitely find a way.

464
00:21:57,560 --> 00:21:59,360
What evil sins.

465
00:22:01,040 --> 00:22:02,240
Although it's wrong

466
00:22:02,240 --> 00:22:03,480
to have a mistress who's a singer,

467
00:22:03,920 --> 00:22:05,840
he shouldn't have been so ruthless as to do this either.

468
00:22:07,520 --> 00:22:09,240
New wounds pile on old scars.

469
00:22:10,120 --> 00:22:13,240
No matter what, you are still his flesh and blood.

470
00:22:14,560 --> 00:22:16,160
If something goes wrong,

471
00:22:17,200 --> 00:22:18,480
what is he to do?

472
00:22:19,800 --> 00:22:21,040
I'm fine, Nanny.

473
00:22:21,040 --> 00:22:23,160
These wounds will be okay after a few days.

474
00:22:24,800 --> 00:22:26,280
Since you were young until now,

475
00:22:26,280 --> 00:22:27,800
you have been beaten many times.

476
00:22:28,880 --> 00:22:30,240
You have been always beaten into this state.

477
00:22:33,040 --> 00:22:36,080
Not, not every time.

478
00:22:37,440 --> 00:22:38,360
Seriously.

479
00:22:40,280 --> 00:22:43,120
It's too cruel. Too cruel!

480
00:22:45,160 --> 00:22:46,840
It's also my fault

481
00:22:46,840 --> 00:22:49,240
for being such a disappointment.

482
00:22:49,960 --> 00:22:51,080
Wait.

483
00:22:55,080 --> 00:22:56,680
Where did you get this scar from?

484
00:22:57,360 --> 00:22:58,080
I don't remember you

485
00:22:58,080 --> 00:22:59,000
had this before.

486
00:22:59,480 --> 00:23:00,720
This is not a scar

487
00:23:00,720 --> 00:23:02,320
you can get from beatings.

488
00:23:03,080 --> 00:23:04,680
Young Master, stop hiding this from me.

489
00:23:04,680 --> 00:23:05,480
Tell me.

490
00:23:05,720 --> 00:23:07,160
How did you get this?

491
00:23:08,880 --> 00:23:09,800
Three years ago,

492
00:23:10,840 --> 00:23:12,160
a brother from the Fifth Branch House

493
00:23:12,200 --> 00:23:13,400
took an interest in a maid.

494
00:23:15,480 --> 00:23:16,350
The maid refused his advances,

495
00:23:16,350 --> 00:23:17,320
so he forced himself upon her.

496
00:23:18,360 --> 00:23:19,680
The maid was fiercely virtuous,

497
00:23:19,680 --> 00:23:21,480
in the end she committed suicide.

498
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:23,680
They put the blame on me.

499
00:23:24,280 --> 00:23:25,800
But the dead cannot bear witness.

500
00:23:26,840 --> 00:23:28,240
The manor of a Marquis

501
00:23:28,640 --> 00:23:30,560
is no better than a jail.

502
00:23:30,990 --> 00:23:32,960
It's hell. It's almost purgatory!

503
00:23:33,790 --> 00:23:35,720
They were purposefully wanting you to die,

504
00:23:36,520 --> 00:23:38,080
scheming for your wealth and assets.

505
00:23:40,210 --> 00:23:43,280
Nanny, what do you mean by "wanting me to die"

506
00:23:43,280 --> 00:23:44,280
and "scheming for my wealth"?

507
00:23:44,560 --> 00:23:46,360
You sound like you're telling stories.

508
00:23:48,400 --> 00:23:49,825
Young Master, you are after all the child

509
00:23:49,825 --> 00:23:51,320
of a legal wife in the Manor of the Marquis.

510
00:23:52,400 --> 00:23:55,600
Moreover, that Mistress Qin,

511
00:23:55,960 --> 00:23:57,440
she treats you very well.

512
00:23:58,400 --> 00:23:59,680
Hence, there are some things

513
00:24:01,560 --> 00:24:03,280
I meant to keep to myself

514
00:24:04,280 --> 00:24:07,920
and take them to my coffin to see First Miss.

515
00:24:16,240 --> 00:24:17,840
If you don't wish to hear it, Young Master.

516
00:24:18,680 --> 00:24:19,880
I will just not say it.

517
00:24:29,200 --> 00:24:30,160
I will hear it.

518
00:24:32,510 --> 00:24:33,600
You must find it strange

519
00:24:34,800 --> 00:24:36,050
how was it that your mother,

520
00:24:36,050 --> 00:24:37,640
who was the daughter of salt merchant,

521
00:24:38,520 --> 00:24:40,560
was able to marry into a Marquis Manor,

522
00:24:41,240 --> 00:24:43,440
and become the main wife, the legitimate Madam.

523
00:24:46,120 --> 00:24:47,440
To be the legitimate wife,

524
00:24:47,440 --> 00:24:49,000
it matters that the two houses match each other in status.

525
00:24:49,760 --> 00:24:51,040
But for a second marriage,

526
00:24:51,040 --> 00:24:52,880
it's not so strict, right?

527
00:24:54,840 --> 00:24:57,280
The Gu House earned their nobility through meritorious service.

528
00:24:57,280 --> 00:24:58,800
They earned their death-pardoning medallion.

529
00:25:00,120 --> 00:25:01,275
If it hadn't been due to a great calamity

530
00:25:01,275 --> 00:25:01,800
that was upon them,

531
00:25:02,600 --> 00:25:04,840
they wouldn't have married with a merchant family.

532
00:25:07,480 --> 00:25:08,560
What calamity?

533
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:12,600
The Old Master,

534
00:25:12,600 --> 00:25:14,440
he built a business empire all on his own.

535
00:25:15,800 --> 00:25:17,840
He only had a sole child, your mother, the First Miss.

536
00:25:18,600 --> 00:25:22,600
He knew the Bai's residing in the southern village

537
00:25:22,600 --> 00:25:23,425
would banish

538
00:25:23,425 --> 00:25:25,440
and kill even orphans and widows.

539
00:25:25,460 --> 00:25:26,360
They could not be relied upon.

540
00:25:27,600 --> 00:25:29,240
So he wanted to seek

541
00:25:29,240 --> 00:25:30,680
a good marriage for the young Miss.

542
00:25:31,800 --> 00:25:33,800
It didn't matter

543
00:25:33,800 --> 00:25:35,160
if it was a humble family or wealthy one.

544
00:25:35,720 --> 00:25:38,120
What mattered was whether they would be good to the Miss.

545
00:25:39,280 --> 00:25:41,280
He was willing to give a lavish dowry

546
00:25:41,280 --> 00:25:42,360
to accompany her in marriage.

547
00:25:43,120 --> 00:25:45,160
At that time,

548
00:25:45,160 --> 00:25:47,720
suddenly someone from the capital paid a visit.

549
00:25:48,800 --> 00:25:50,760
The visitor said a merit-earned noble house

550
00:25:50,760 --> 00:25:53,920
in Dongjing was seeking a marriage.

551
00:25:54,920 --> 00:25:57,400
They had found out that our Miss

552
00:25:57,440 --> 00:25:58,640
was virtuous and gentle.

553
00:25:59,280 --> 00:26:01,480
The matchmaker made it sound like a match in heaven.

554
00:26:02,120 --> 00:26:03,560
But the Old Master had already found out

555
00:26:04,360 --> 00:26:05,360
the one that came to seek marriage

556
00:26:06,600 --> 00:26:07,050
was asking it for

557
00:26:07,050 --> 00:26:08,040
the Fourth and Fifth sons of the Marquis.

558
00:26:08,040 --> 00:26:09,480
Go slowly.

559
00:26:09,840 --> 00:26:11,000
Go slowly now, Fourth Master.

560
00:26:11,440 --> 00:26:13,520
Come often.

561
00:26:13,560 --> 00:26:15,560
For you.

562
00:26:15,560 --> 00:26:16,160
Take it.

563
00:26:16,640 --> 00:26:18,720
One was whoring frequently,

564
00:26:18,720 --> 00:26:20,040
and the other was haughty and rude.

565
00:26:20,880 --> 00:26:23,480
