00:37:17,640 --> 00:37:18,520
Madam

850
00:37:26,080 --> 00:37:28,360
A year after your mother passed away,

851
00:37:30,040 --> 00:37:32,400
the Marquis hurriedly married

852
00:37:32,400 --> 00:37:33,800
the younger sister of the Qin first wife.

853
00:37:34,440 --> 00:37:35,360
Don't say anymore.

854
00:37:36,800 --> 00:37:38,080
Could it be a misunderstanding?

855
00:37:41,280 --> 00:37:43,350
Could you have heard wrong

856
00:37:43,350 --> 00:37:44,960
or remembered wrong?

857
00:37:47,680 --> 00:37:49,120
I told you everything I saw

858
00:37:49,160 --> 00:37:50,160
with my own eyes.

859
00:37:51,590 --> 00:37:53,120
Not one bit of it is wrong.

860
00:37:54,120 --> 00:37:55,600
These years, these matters,

861
00:37:56,960 --> 00:37:57,800
they rolled over

862
00:37:57,800 --> 00:37:59,160
again and again in my mind.

863
00:38:00,600 --> 00:38:02,480
I remember them very clearly.

864
00:38:19,800 --> 00:38:20,920
Rest up, Nanny.

865
00:38:51,360 --> 00:38:53,300
Looking at the beauty under the candlelight is just like

866
00:38:53,300 --> 00:38:55,120
looking at the flower under the moonlight.

867
00:38:55,360 --> 00:38:56,560
What a sight it is.

868
00:38:58,960 --> 00:39:00,040
I'm old now.

869
00:39:01,020 --> 00:39:02,000
Not old.

870
00:39:03,280 --> 00:39:04,800
Even if a few more decades go by,

871
00:39:04,872 --> 00:39:06,000
to me

872
00:39:06,000 --> 00:39:06,920
you're still a beauty.

873
00:39:08,960 --> 00:39:10,640
Do you really mean it?

874
00:39:10,640 --> 00:39:12,720
If you meet a younger and more beautiful one,

875
00:39:12,825 --> 00:39:14,040
won't you be enticed?

876
00:39:17,080 --> 00:39:18,200
Beauties are plenty.

877
00:39:22,600 --> 00:39:24,480
But a beauty with so much talent

878
00:39:24,480 --> 00:39:27,240
and understanding is a rarity.

879
00:39:28,120 --> 00:39:31,560
Shuang'er, in my heart,

880
00:39:32,240 --> 00:39:34,040
you're always the best.

881
00:39:38,600 --> 00:39:40,160
I remember that day.

882
00:39:40,160 --> 00:39:42,000
I was doing needlework with the Old Madam.

883
00:39:42,920 --> 00:39:45,680
You lifted up the curtain and came in,

884
00:39:45,680 --> 00:39:47,840
bringing with you a breeze of jasmine scent.

885
00:39:49,480 --> 00:39:50,600
I will never forget

886
00:39:50,640 --> 00:39:51,920
that image of you then.

887
00:39:54,160 --> 00:39:56,320
This lifetime, following you,

888
00:39:56,320 --> 00:39:57,200
I have no complaint.

889
00:40:01,560 --> 00:40:05,280
Shuang'er, I shall never let you regret.

890
00:40:10,320 --> 00:40:11,800
I shall never regret.

891
00:40:13,000 --> 00:40:16,080
Feng'er and Mo'er are both so obedient,

892
00:40:16,080 --> 00:40:17,600
and I often think at night

893
00:40:18,440 --> 00:40:19,120
that this all is a good life

894
00:40:19,120 --> 00:40:20,520
you've given me.

895
00:40:23,880 --> 00:40:28,040
Just that lately Mo'er often cries

896
00:40:28,920 --> 00:40:30,200
and I'm afraid she will ruin her health by crying.

897
00:40:31,640 --> 00:40:32,880
What's wrong with her suddenly?

898
00:40:35,560 --> 00:40:37,360
It's all due to that she lost your face

899
00:40:37,360 --> 00:40:39,560
before the Countess a few days ago.

900
00:40:42,960 --> 00:40:44,640
That's not her fault,

901
00:40:44,640 --> 00:40:46,120
and I've already looked into it to clear her.

902
00:40:47,120 --> 00:40:48,200
It was Rulan and Minglan,

903
00:40:48,240 --> 00:40:49,880
those two girls who are troublesome.

904
00:40:50,800 --> 00:40:52,440
But the court Nanny from the palace is here.

905
00:40:52,840 --> 00:40:54,080
And she's teaching rules to Rulan and Minglan,

906
00:40:54,120 --> 00:40:55,520
but she won't let Mo'er attend.

907
00:40:55,960 --> 00:40:57,160
Those two are senseless

908
00:40:57,160 --> 00:40:59,040
and they need to be taught,

909
00:40:59,360 --> 00:41:01,120
but Molan is most sensible.

910
00:41:01,880 --> 00:41:03,320
She needn't go.

911
00:41:03,320 --> 00:41:05,240
She can just continue with the academy lessons.

912
00:41:08,360 --> 00:41:09,760
But Molan

913
00:41:09,760 --> 00:41:11,560
still did go to the front hall.

914
00:41:12,360 --> 00:41:14,120
Her temperament is like mine.

915
00:41:14,120 --> 00:41:15,400
Just too soft.

916
00:41:16,000 --> 00:41:17,520
She should actually listen to

917
00:41:17,520 --> 00:41:19,320
the palace Nanny's teaching.

918
00:41:20,320 --> 00:41:22,600
But since you dote on me,

919
00:41:23,120 --> 00:41:25,160
Big Madam chased me out

920
00:41:25,160 --> 00:41:26,600
and scolded me,

921
00:41:26,960 --> 00:41:30,440
saying I'm always seducing you.

922
00:41:32,440 --> 00:41:33,400
She scolded you again?

923
00:41:35,360 --> 00:41:36,360
That's nothing to worry about.

924
00:41:37,390 --> 00:41:40,080
Just my Mo'er is pitiful.

925
00:41:41,440 --> 00:41:45,480
Pity that she's noble.

926
00:41:45,480 --> 00:41:47,880
But since she just had to be born from me.

927
00:41:48,170 --> 00:41:49,560
she doesn't even get to listen to

928
00:41:49,600 --> 00:41:50,640
lessons about lady rules.

929
00:41:52,000 --> 00:41:54,040
I just loathe that

930
00:41:54,040 --> 00:41:56,640
we met too late.

931
00:41:56,920 --> 00:41:58,480
You were already with a wife

932
00:41:58,480 --> 00:41:59,920
and I couldn't bear to leave you.

933
00:42:00,400 --> 00:42:03,520
So I could only become your concubine,

934
00:42:03,760 --> 00:42:05,800
and I've compromised my own children.

935
00:42:07,240 --> 00:42:09,840
If my Mo'er were born from Big Madam's belly,

936
00:42:09,840 --> 00:42:12,920
how great would it be?

937
00:42:19,560 --> 00:42:20,200
Alright.

938
00:42:23,320 --> 00:42:24,120
No crying.

939
00:42:26,440 --> 00:42:27,280
Look at you.

940
00:42:36,040 --> 00:42:37,200
That's punishment.

941
00:42:37,200 --> 00:42:38,600
It's not some great honor.

942
00:42:39,360 --> 00:42:40,120
Don't be sad.

943
00:42:41,760 --> 00:42:42,680
Alright.

944
00:42:43,390 --> 00:42:45,680
Darling,

945
00:42:45,680 --> 00:42:47,800
I'm a lowly servant by origin.

946
00:42:48,880 --> 00:42:50,720
I fear I will ruin

947
00:42:50,720 --> 00:42:51,960
Mo'er's match.

948
00:42:52,450 --> 00:42:54,080
Mo'er is outstanding

949
00:42:54,080 --> 00:42:54,920
but that's still not enough.

950
00:42:55,320 --> 00:42:57,520
It's all up to Big Madam.

951
00:42:58,960 --> 00:43:00,400
Hong. Tell me.

952
00:43:02,600 --> 00:43:05,920
Does Big Madam hate you

953
00:43:05,960 --> 00:43:07,040
because I'm pampered,

954
00:43:07,200 --> 00:43:08,520
and that's why

955
00:43:08,520 --> 00:43:09,760
she won't let Mo'er go listen to the lessons?

956
00:43:09,840 --> 00:43:11,240
She can’t make decisions for me yet!

957
00:43:15,040 --> 00:43:15,840
It's true.

958
00:43:16,600 --> 00:43:18,520
In this house,

959
00:43:18,520 --> 00:43:20,360
you are still the Master.
